OL,3,CBriton jailed in Iran given extra two-
OL,4,Cyear sentence, family says
OL,6,FThe family of a British man jailed in
OL,7,FIran on spying charges says he has
OL,8,Fbeen sentenced to an additional two
OL,9,Fyears in prison.
OL,11,FCraig Foreman and his wife Lindsay
OL,12,Fwere sentenced to 10 years' prison in
OL,13,FFebruary after being convicted of
OL,14,Fespionage, charges they both deny.
OL,16,FAccording to his family, Mr Foreman
OL,17,Fwas told he had been given an
OL,18,Fadditional two-year sentence for
OL,19,Fspeaking to media outlets.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
