OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784107113
OL,3,CBriton jailed in Iran given extra two-
OL,4,Cyear sentence, family says
OL,6,FThe couple, from East Sussex, were
OL,7,Farrested in January 2025 while
OL,8,Ftravelling through Iran during an
OL,9,Faround-the-world motorcycle trip. They
OL,10,Fare being held in Tehran's Evin prison.
OL,12,FTheir son, Joe Bennett, said the
OL,13,Ffamily was "extremely concerned" by
OL,14,Fthe reports.
OL,16,F"We have received extremely concerning
OL,17,Freports that Craig has been sentenced
OL,18,Fto a further two years in prison," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@uD@LOUuD@`O]xD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784107113
OL,3,CBriton jailed in Iran given extra two-
OL,4,Cyear sentence, family says
OL,6,F"We understand he was told he was
OL,7,Fbeing taken to see his lawyer but was
OL,8,Finstead brought before a judge and
OL,9,Finformed of the additional sentence.
OL,11,F"Despite requests, he was allowed no
OL,12,Flawyer, no translator and no
OL,13,Fopportunity to defend himself. He was
OL,14,Ftold the two years had been added
OL,15,Fbecause he had spoken to the press.
OL,17,F"We didn't think we could be any more
OL,18,Fshocked at their appalling treatment,
OL,19,Fbut in this case we are absolutely
OL,20,Fflabbergasted."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
