OL,3,CBriton jailed in Iran given extra two-
OL,4,Cyear sentence, family says
OL,6,FIn June, the couple's family said the
OL,7,Fpair had lost an appeal against their
OL,8,Fconvictions and were unable to attend
OL,9,Ftheir appeal hearing.
OL,11,FMr Bennett said Mr Foreman was on the
OL,12,F68th day of a hunger strike, while his
OL,13,Fwife was on her 59th.
OL,15,FTheir family said a letter asking them
OL,16,Fto end their hunger strike had not
OL,17,Fbeen delivered.
OL,19,FMr Bennett added: "We are asking, with
OL,20,Feverything we have, for them to be
OL,21,Fshown mercy and allowed to come home."
OL,26,@{D@SOU}D@fO]
